{"tid":959123,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"【創作分享】兩毫砌金畫 再噴出《梅艷芳》","createTime":"2018-12-28T10:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T10:03:44.000Z","uid":143257,"like":136,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"94cfeb54bb693e22a38627ab8c15a8043c15ed57","tid":959123,"uid":143257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T10:43:50.000Z","msg":"小弟之前開post講過 樹葉 繁體中文字 作品<br />\n今次post係關於[ 兩毫 ]既創作<br />\n係post圖之前，其實我想講講點解我會選擇呢三種東西作為創作媒介<br />\n簡單黎講，樹葉/兩毫/繁體中文字 都係一啲因社會進步，而逐漸消失或遺忘既野<br />\n自從電子貨幣發達後，現金 尤其硬幣(兩毫)係現今社會就好似雞肋一樣，食之無味，用之不著，棄之可惜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次呢幅作品大概係我兩毫作品的第五次創作，頭四幅作品一直都係一早分好左兩種兩毫(金/黑)，所以想搞搞新意思，亦想再挑戰下自己同物料的可塑性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mfu2E0eaaJo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fmfu2E0eaaJo&d=JSnEAddLjxlMXR%2BXYQ2aFKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=904a5bb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mfu2E0eaaJo</a><br />\nig片 link : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Br6Vabfger2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBr6Vabfger2%2F&d=JSnEAddLjxlMXR%2BXYQ2aFKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=b35dd5f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBr6Vabfger2%2F&h=b3651374\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/Br6Vabfger2/</a><br />\n<br />\n『斜陽無限 無奈只一息間燦爛，隨雲霞漸散 逝去的光彩不復還』<br />\n<br />\n呢句係夕陽之歌既歌詞，由梅豔芳主唱，雖然我覺得連登未必好多人聽過，但其實呢首歌間接令我諗到呢次作品既新呈現方式『逝去的光彩不復還(毫子變色)』。講起梅艷芳，當然我覺得自己算唔上係佢既歌迷，只係屬於中意聽佢既歌，而我覺得梅艷芳作為一個台上表演者真係一流，佢表演既態度前無古人 後無來者，不是為名，亦不是為利。純粹係為左表演同娛樂給台下既觀眾，又可能同梅艷芳個人背景同時代背景有關，點都好 真係好欣賞佢。欣賞佢個種享受過程而不追求結果既態度。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/28/113223_dab04bd40c779b00bca7c0829ed75c6d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F28%2F113223_dab04bd40c779b00bca7c0829ed75c6d.JPG&h=d4f69c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NUv8ny6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNUv8ny6.jpg&h=426b0731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ihTU2yZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FihTU2yZ.jpg&h=e1b11512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而今次作品我覺得最正同最期待既亦係過程，一幅全部金色既兩毫作品，當然我砌既時候已經分左兩種唔同既兩毫(正常的/經處理的)，而兩種都係金色既毫子，砌既時候好似一支透明墨水筆畫畫咁。噴上化學藥水後，部分兩毫變黑，令作品內容慢慢浮出黎。其實整個變色過程只不過4-5分鐘到，30秒已經開始睇得出。其實我本身都冇預算個作品效果會咁明顯，因為第一次咁做，真心親眼望住變色個下覺得好興奮，已經開始期待下次作品。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後如果大家中意同想睇多d 不如follow 我art.ig 同facebook page<br />\n當支持下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nig : gllh_art <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/gllh_art/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgllh_art%2F&d=JSnEAddLjxlMXR%2BXYQ2aFKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=49fbe4c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/gllh_art/</a><br />\nfb page : Giraffe leung lok hei  <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gllhart/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgllhart%2F&d=JSnEAddLjxlMXR%2BXYQ2aFKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=9a5f0a6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/gllhart/</a>"},{"pid":"7a28521f70be82af31cbb6252765228f0daa8d03","tid":959123,"uid":35637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df015bdc60bcc1554db7f934430f07bce0ded48","tid":959123,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"